</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>away_mode</code></td>
<td>no</td>
<td>New value of away mode. â€˜onâ€™/â€˜offâ€™ or True/False</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<h4>Automation example</h4>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">automation:
  trigger:
    platform: time
    at: &quot;07:15:00&quot;
  action:
    - service: water_heater.set_away_mode
      data:
        entity_id: water_heater.demo
        away_mode: true
